  "content": "<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.8LYPguczQUxUtxHF]{UM5 Ch.6: Armor}</p>\n<p>UM5 p.92</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">These modifications are available to most armors (including all exo-armors) and often have requirements for their addition. There is no limit to the number of modifications you can add to exo-armor, though non exo</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">-armor is generally limited to 1 for light, 2 for medium and 3 for heavy.&nbsp;<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Armors that already have the system cannot add a second version except to upgrade an existing system, as stated in the description.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.oW9iuEoxWvtPKvDo]{UM5 Ch.6: Tech Level 0-5} @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-equipment.JKcEAJ4xm2Us5hYN]{Battry Cell, High}</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\" style=\"height: 357px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 393px; height: 17px;\"><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">ARMOR </span></strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 80px; height: 17px;\"><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">COST </span></strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 17px;\"><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">STEALTH </span></strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 48px; height: 17px;\"><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">WT. </span></strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 39px; height: 17px;\"><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">CELL </span></strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 31px; height: 17px;\"><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">TL</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 393px; height: 17px;\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-equipment.I1HPD8pjZDmxfTVJ]{Auto-Reload (exo only)}&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 80px; height: 17px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">1,000 </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 17px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Disadvantage </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 48px; height: 17p